request.description:
# Get Manager Information

This endpoint allows you to retrieve information about a manager.

## Request

`POST /api/getManagerInfo/`

### Request Body
- Form-Data
  - `Code`: (text) The code of the manager.

## Response

- Status: 400
- Content-Type: text/html

Example response:
```json
{
    "Status": 0,
    "Manager": {
        "Code": 0,
        "Name": "",
        "Family": "",
        "SirName": "",
        "NaCode": "",
        "Phone": "",
        "Character": {
            "Code": 0,
            "Name": "",
            "AccessLevel": 0
        },
        "Password": "",
        "RegisterTime": "",
        "AccessLocation": [
            {
                "Code": 0,
                "Name": "",
                "Type": 0
            }
        ]
    }
}
```
```json
{
    "Status": 0,
    "Message": ""
}
```
